00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:42,960
The Prince of Tennis
~ Match! Tennis Juniors! ~

21
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:53,600
[Yu Qing students] Yu Qing, come on.
Yu Qing, come on.

22
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:56,160
[somber music]

23
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:04,160
[Yu Qing students] Yu Qing, come on.
Yu Qing, come on.

24
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:05,240
[sighs]

25
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:08,400
TIAN ZILONG

26
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,639
THIS IS THE CLIP OF THE MATCH.

27
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:12,160
YU QING IS A WORTHY RIVAL,
BUT HAI GUANG WON'T SLACK OFF.

28
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,280
DON'T WORRY.

29
00:02:14,919 --> 00:02:16,920
[somber music]

30
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:18,640
I HAVEN'T PLAYED TENNIS FOR A LONG TIME.

31
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:20,480
TAKE CARE.

32
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,240
[Siyang] Captain Bai?

33
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:26,680
BAI SHITING
CAPTAIN OF HAI GUANG

34
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,400
I didn't expect to meet you here.

35
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:38,520
Oh. Have you stayed here...

36
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:40,920
for a long time?

37
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:41,840
Yes.

38
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:45,960
Hospitalization for a long time
will be kind of boring.

39
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:47,760
[sighs]

40
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,720
Do you like to frown?

41
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,360
Oh.

42
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:52,880
I'm used to it.

43
00:02:55,240 --> 00:03:00,080
Indeed, it's hard to relax
with something to worry about.

44
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:04,800
[inhales sharply]
There's nothing to worry about now.

45
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:07,520
It's better to get rid of this habit.

46
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:12,120
Sometimes, I tell myself to relax,

47
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:15,600
but something bad always happens.

48
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,040
Right?

49
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,680
You're right.

50
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:23,040
I chose to believe in them,

51
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:26,240
so I have to believe
that no matter what happens,

52
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:28,640
there is always a way out.

53
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,560
How is your arm?

54
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:36,840
[sighs]

55
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,120
I hope that it will recover.

56
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:43,200
[exhales sharply]
It's good.

57
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,040
Your sickness...

58
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:48,040
[somber music]

59
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:49,880
If you don't know the direction,

60
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:52,480
seeing the sun on the horizon,

61
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:56,160
you won't know if it is rising or setting.

62
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,280
[Shiting] If you know the direction,

63
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:04,080
you will know that
sunlight will disappear sooner or later...

64
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:08,760
and it will eventually get dark.

65
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:15,120
[Siyang] You're right. But...

66
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:18,880
the sun will rise the next day.

67
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,880
You're so optimistic.

68
00:04:23,399 --> 00:04:24,720
If we met earlier,

69
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,760
maybe we could have been good friends.

70
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,080
[soft chuckle]

71
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:31,760
Unfortunately, we are now rivals
that can't play in the match.

72
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,360
[breathes deeply]

73
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:38,160
I hope you and your team
can return to the court.

74
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:43,440
As a rival, I look forward
to having an official match with you.

75
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,600
Me too.

76
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,560
-[snickers]
-[sighs]

77
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:55,560
These guys in Hai Guang...

78
00:04:57,840 --> 00:04:58,840
I will go and find them.

79
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:00,880
Wait a minute.

80
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,400
What's wrong?

81
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,000
I will go with you.

82
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:08,360
Other patients complained
about the noise. Be quiet!

83
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:11,920
-Captain?
-Captain, it's great that you're fine.

84
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:15,560
Oh. The doctor said
that after resting for some time,

85
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,520
I can be discharged from the hospital.

86
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:20,320
Remember to learn and to train hard.

87
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,960
[Tang Jiale] Captain, we do practice hard.

88
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:26,480
Today, we came after training.

89
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:28,000
Don't worry, Siyang.

90
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:29,760
We will keep working hard.

91
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:31,840
When you return,
let's fight against Hai Guang.

92
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,920
Mm-hm.

93
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,840
I believe that Yu Qing can go further.

94
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:40,680
In the following days of my absence,
I will leave it to you all.

95
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,280
-Mm-hm.
-Mm-hm.

96
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:49,360
[Jingwu] Siyang,

97
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:52,760
I heard that it takes a long time
to register and see a doctor there.

98
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,200
I contacted the hospital.

99
00:05:56,440 --> 00:05:58,240
They will get the best doctor for you.

100
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:00,600
Oh.

101
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:04,360
For the accommodation,
don't refuse my help.

102
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:07,480
I don't usually stay in houses abroad,

103
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:09,480
but it's okay for you to stay there.

104
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,560
Okay. Thank you.

105
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,440
For that matter,

106
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:16,240
I will deal with it
as soon as I get back to school.

107
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,600
I will inform you if there's any update.

108
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:19,800
Ji Jingwu,

109
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:23,720
if Xing Yao needs my help,

110
00:06:24,320 --> 00:06:25,320
please tell me.

111
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:26,960
By the way...

112
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:28,360
Um...

113
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:30,800
There is one thing.

114
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:32,760
Go ahead.

115
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,240
[exhales deeply]

116
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:41,640
I'm sorry...

117
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:44,400
for that match.

118
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:47,080
It's not your fault. Besides,

119
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:49,680
don't apologize for anything in the match.

120
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:53,200
Yu Qing will wait for Xing Yao
at the nationals.

121
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:54,800
Sure.

122
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:59,120
Let's play a match fairly.

123
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:01,720
I'll wait for you.

124
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:03,480
It's a deal.

125
00:07:05,840 --> 00:07:07,200
OUTPATIENT SERVICE

126
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,080
[Siyang] Doctor.

127
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:12,960
[sighs]

128
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,320
Have you completed
the discharge procedure?

129
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:17,680
Yes.

130
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:23,200
When we first met,
you were just in Grade 10.

131
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:28,000
I told you not to practice excessively,

132
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:30,840
or it will seriously hurt your arm.

133
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:33,080
You told me that
if you don't practice more,

134
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:34,920
your dreams can't be realized,

135
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,600
that you should go all out.

136
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,200
If you had followed my advice,

137
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:43,600
there wouldn't be these problems.

138
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,440
[sighs]

139
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:50,040
However, I want to congratulate you
for realizing your dream.

140
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:53,120
Thanks for your efforts
during this period.

141
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:56,360
Though I didn't see any matches in person,

142
00:07:56,840 --> 00:08:00,560
I witnessed your efforts in another way.

143
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:04,800
If there is anything you want to do,
just go for it.

144
00:08:05,760 --> 00:08:08,400
When you are abroad,
concentrate on getting treatment.

145
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:11,520
There's another thing,

146
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:16,080
but I haven't decided how to handle it.

147
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:20,880
As long as you want to do it,
you can, right?

148
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:25,560
Thank you for your care all this time.

149
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:29,120
-I'll see you again.
-Don't say "I'll see you again."

150
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,360
If we don't meet again,

151
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:33,840
it means that
your arm recovered completely.

152
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:35,799
[breathes deeply]

153
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:38,080
Then, take care.

154
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,080
Mm-hm.

155
00:08:46,280 --> 00:08:48,280
[birds chirping]

156
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:10,960
[playful music]

157
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:12,600
Hey.

158
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:19,200
Why did you ask me to come in secret?

159
00:09:20,560 --> 00:09:23,560
After seeing the performance
of Golden Partners,

160
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:27,400
I started to consider my tennis career.

161
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:30,800
Did you finally figure it out?

162
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:34,120
What do you mean?

163
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:35,760
[sighs]

164
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:40,240
I thought you finally decided
to give up tennis.

165
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:41,880
Of course not!

166
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:45,120
Tennis is what I will strive for
all my life.

167
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:49,160
However, after thorough consideration,

168
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:52,560
I think doubles is more suitable for me,

169
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:55,520
while singles easily reveal my weakness.

170
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:57,040
Doubles?

171
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:59,280
Who will be your partner?

172
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:02,240
[quirky music]

173
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:12,640
Do you mean me?

174
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:17,280
Have more confidence in yourself.

175
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,000
[sighs]

176
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:23,160
We have no confidence in ourselves.

177
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:24,360
Don't worry.

178
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:27,160
I found some tips
for improving tennis skills.

179
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:38,080
[quirky music]

180
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,520
What do you see in this picture?

181
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:45,480
I see people and a dog.

182
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:48,360
[clicks tongue]
You are so simpleminded and weak.

183
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:51,640
Don't you realize how they developed
chemistry with each other?

184
00:10:58,440 --> 00:11:00,240
[Huang Jing] What can you see
in Dachi's eyes?

185
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:02,280
It's concentration.

186
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:04,680
It's supreme concentration.

187
00:11:06,520 --> 00:11:07,720
He's observing this dog

188
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:12,280
because the dog is cooperating with Jiale
like a mushroom growing after the rain.

189
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:17,440
[gasps]
Mushrooms...

190
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:20,640
Aren't they my favorite springtime food?

191
00:11:21,280 --> 00:11:22,200
No.

192
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:29,760
Dachi is learning from this dog.

193
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:32,120
Don't you feel ashamed? Huh?

194
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:35,120
Why can't you learn from this dog?

195
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:37,080
Go along with me.

196
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:38,440
[sighs]

197
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,440
I agree with you.

198
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,400
You know yourself well.

199
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:47,120
[sighs]

200
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:52,120
What's wrong? Why are you silent?

201
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:54,120
I'm just thinking...

202
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:58,800
if I should first train a dog as they did.

203
00:11:59,800 --> 00:12:02,080
I think it is better
to train ourselves hard.

204
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:03,200
You are wrong.

205
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:07,120
We can't catch up to others
by just training hard.

206
00:12:07,640 --> 00:12:11,640
Those who can become official players
must have secret ways of training.

207
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:14,640
What kinds of secret ways?

208
00:12:15,560 --> 00:12:16,440
Think about it.

209
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,560
Captain loves fishing.

210
00:12:20,920 --> 00:12:22,000
Yan Zhiming loves juicing.

211
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:24,160
Baiyang loves running.

212
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:25,960
Xinglong loves cooking.

213
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:27,960
Dachi and Jiale love playing frisbee.

214
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:30,960
Zhuo Zhi loves his younger brother.

215
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:33,160
Did you find any commonalities?

216
00:12:34,680 --> 00:12:35,520
No.

217
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:37,960
They have other hobbies besides tennis.

218
00:12:38,760 --> 00:12:42,160
Maybe these hobbies have some connections
with tennis.

219
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:48,680
Do you mean that we can't play tennis well
because we don't have any hobbies?

220
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:49,960
You said it!

221
00:12:51,920 --> 00:12:53,840
But Lu Xia doesn't have any hobbies.

222
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:54,760
[Huang Jing] Hey.

223
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:57,280
That's because he's good at pretending.
No one knows yet.

224
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:59,840
So we have to have hobbies.

225
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,120
Don't worry. I made preparations.

226
00:13:05,640 --> 00:13:08,560
This is our starting point
of becoming the main players of the team.

227
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:11,640
Mm-hm.

228
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:14,320
[doorbell rings]

229
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:17,240
[playful music]

230
00:13:20,760 --> 00:13:22,120
[Xiangqian] Wait a minute.

231
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:36,040
Who are you?

232
00:13:38,080 --> 00:13:40,920
Hello, is Mr. Lu Xiangqian home?

233
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:44,480
Huh?

234
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:46,800
-Are you Captain Siyang?
-Are you okay?

235
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:52,040
I'm fine. We'll eat hot pot tonight.
I'm making charcoal.

236
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:54,000
-Oh.
-[Xiangqian] Why are you here?

237
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:56,440
Why didn't you go to school today?

238
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:57,880
I asked for sick leave.

239
00:13:58,240 --> 00:14:01,120
Mr. Lu, I want to talk to you
about Lu Xia.

240
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:04,000
Okay. Please come in.

241
00:14:04,640 --> 00:14:07,080
Mm-hm.
[coughs]

242
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:12,560
[Xiangqian] Hurry up and eat.

243
00:14:15,280 --> 00:14:16,120
Mm-mm.

244
00:14:16,520 --> 00:14:18,320
Don't eat it if you don't like it.

245
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:24,160
Put the pineapple down.
It is not cooked thoroughly.

246
00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:26,240
[quirky music]

247
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:31,600
Well...
[clears throat]

248
00:14:32,920 --> 00:14:34,960
are you going out tomorrow?

249
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,640
If you'll stay at home,

250
00:14:37,160 --> 00:14:41,320
I want to build a cat kennel for Karubin
in the backyard.

251
00:14:41,960 --> 00:14:44,000
If you are free, come and help me.

252
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:45,720
I will go train tomorrow.

253
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:50,880
Your captain is absent.
It's okay to fool around.

254
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:52,720
You can practice at home.

255
00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:55,240
We have to train together
under such circumstances.

256
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:57,640
We can't make the captain worry about us.

257
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:59,280
It's not like you.

258
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:01,960
[Xiangqian]
Oh. It seems that you enjoy it a lot.

259
00:15:02,520 --> 00:15:05,760
You were feeling blue before.

260
00:15:06,600 --> 00:15:07,800
I like playing tennis.

261
00:15:11,920 --> 00:15:12,880
Is it wrong?

262
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:17,800
No. You're right.
I will do it on my own tomorrow.

263
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:23,000
Then after training,
will you go fishing with me?

264
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:24,960
No, I won't.

265
00:15:25,320 --> 00:15:28,160
Okay. Anything you say.
It's tomorrow noon, right? It's a deal.

266
00:15:29,040 --> 00:15:30,400
[Xiangqian] If you are done,

267
00:15:30,720 --> 00:15:33,800
let's drink and then you can go to sleep.

268
00:15:35,560 --> 00:15:36,800
[sighs]

269
00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:43,040
The watermelon is fully cooked.
Why don't you give it a try?

270
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:00,880
Hey, Siyang.

271
00:16:02,360 --> 00:16:05,360
How about going fishing
tomorrow afternoon?

272
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:09,680
[Lu Xia] Are you ready?

273
00:16:11,240 --> 00:16:12,120
Are you ready?

274
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:13,560
[Xiangqian] I'm ready!

275
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:16,120
[chuckles]
I'm ready.

276
00:16:17,160 --> 00:16:18,040
Let's go.

277
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:21,960
Why are you going fishing
with my tennis bag?

278
00:16:22,800 --> 00:16:27,240
I think I can practice tennis with you
when I take a break from fishing.

279
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:28,200
Here.

280
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,360
Did you wash your hands?

281
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:33,360
How dare you say that!

282
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:35,840
Are my hands dirtier than your bag?
Take it.

283
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:37,800
[sighs]

284
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:40,240
Let's go!

285
00:16:41,040 --> 00:16:42,880
[Xiangqian grunting]

286
00:16:43,400 --> 00:16:45,240
[Xiangqian groaning]

287
00:16:45,600 --> 00:16:48,560
The watermelon was not cooked thoroughly
last night.

288
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:50,760
I'm old. I can't eat raw food.

289
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:54,480
I have a stomachache.
[groaning]

290
00:16:54,560 --> 00:16:56,920
[Xiangqian]
Go assemble the fishing rod first.

291
00:16:57,000 --> 00:17:00,120
I will go soon.
[groaning]

292
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:01,480
I wouldn't dare overexert myself.

293
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:03,520
[groans]

294
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:05,200
Go!

295
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:07,160
Are you okay?

296
00:17:08,119 --> 00:17:10,160
[groaning]

297
00:17:11,119 --> 00:17:12,200
[Xiangqian groans]

298
00:17:17,880 --> 00:17:19,119
[chuckles]

299
00:17:20,359 --> 00:17:21,280
[grunts]

300
00:17:34,400 --> 00:17:35,360
[Lu Xia] Captain.

301
00:17:36,840 --> 00:17:37,680
Lu Xia?

302
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:40,560
My father fooled me again.

303
00:17:41,880 --> 00:17:43,560
[sighs]
Have a seat.

304
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:01,440
You don't seem to know how to fish.

305
00:18:03,320 --> 00:18:04,560
He fooled me into coming here.

306
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:10,600
You also came to Yu Qing
because of your father, right?

307
00:18:12,720 --> 00:18:15,160
I joined Yu Qing to break his record
at the national tournament

308
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:17,800
and earn his recognition.

309
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:20,200
[light music]

310
00:18:20,800 --> 00:18:22,200
Did you surpass him?

311
00:18:24,440 --> 00:18:25,760
It doesn't matter now.

312
00:18:26,600 --> 00:18:29,520
I played tennis
because I wanted to defeat him.

313
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,040
[Lu Xia] However...

314
00:18:31,120 --> 00:18:31,960
YU QING THE WINNER

315
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:33,720
...I now have more important things to do.

316
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:42,680
Regardless of happiness,

317
00:18:43,240 --> 00:18:44,440
failures and setbacks,

318
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:46,960
or regrets and sadness,

319
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:50,600
-I want to go with the team until the end.
-Go!

320
00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:52,000
[Yu Qing students] Lu Xia. Lu Xia.

321
00:18:52,080 --> 00:18:54,640
-[Lu Xia] I didn't think about it before.
-Go, Lu Xia!

322
00:18:55,080 --> 00:18:56,240
[all] Be the champion.

323
00:18:58,760 --> 00:19:02,600
[Lu Xia] The team made me realize that
no matter if I can defeat him or not,

324
00:19:03,720 --> 00:19:07,000
I can't give up tennis.

325
00:19:07,080 --> 00:19:11,800
[Yu Qing students]
Go, Yu Qing! Go, Yu Qing!

326
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:20,000
[cheering continues]

327
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:26,520
[crowd cheering]

328
00:19:31,560 --> 00:19:33,560
[light music]

329
00:19:40,000 --> 00:19:41,720
It might be too late to say so,

330
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:46,400
but I want to be Yu Qing's pillar.

331
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:49,320
Can you tell me how to do it?

332
00:19:51,120 --> 00:19:52,160
[exhales sharply]

333
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:56,560
Look at the fishing rod.

334
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:58,160
Without a holder,

335
00:19:58,600 --> 00:20:00,320
the fishing rod wavers in your hand.

336
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:06,640
What you need to do...

337
00:20:08,240 --> 00:20:10,320
is to find your holder.

338
00:20:13,800 --> 00:20:15,520
[gasping]

339
00:20:19,360 --> 00:20:20,320
I didn't bring it.

340
00:20:22,320 --> 00:20:23,200
[chuckles]

341
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:27,680
Let's go. Let's go find your holder.

342
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:35,080
YU QING

343
00:20:39,240 --> 00:20:40,320
[Lu Xia] Is your arm okay?

344
00:20:42,560 --> 00:20:44,080
If you mean my right arm,

345
00:20:44,800 --> 00:20:45,880
it is okay.

346
00:20:47,920 --> 00:20:49,920
[upbeat music]

347
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:53,280
Captain, it is fair this way.

348
00:21:08,960 --> 00:21:09,960
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

349
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:11,800
[Lu Xia grunts]

350
00:21:17,240 --> 00:21:18,320
[clicks tongue]

351
00:21:19,600 --> 00:21:22,680
I wonder if Lu Xia can catch
any fish today.

352
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:27,480
Forget it. It depends on him.

353
00:21:28,360 --> 00:21:30,360
[somber music]

354
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:40,600
[Siyang sighs]

355
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:45,600
[Siyang] Lu Xia,

356
00:21:47,680 --> 00:21:48,520
please remember.

357
00:21:49,120 --> 00:21:51,000
Don't let your record hold you back.

358
00:21:51,800 --> 00:21:53,440
It's already in the past.

359
00:21:53,920 --> 00:21:56,520
You need to think about
how to break your record

360
00:21:57,120 --> 00:21:59,080
using your past experiences.

361
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:03,360
Someday, you can play tennis
in your own style.

362
00:22:05,840 --> 00:22:08,880
Next time, you have to defeat me.

363
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:10,280
When can we play tennis again?

364
00:22:12,720 --> 00:22:13,880
[exhales sharply]

365
00:22:19,080 --> 00:22:22,480
Lu Xia, you will become Yu Qing's pillar.

366
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:30,920
[light music]

367
00:22:42,800 --> 00:22:44,800
[light music continues]

368
00:23:12,280 --> 00:23:13,280
[clicks tongue]

369
00:23:15,040 --> 00:23:19,400
Do you really think that drawing
is going to help us play tennis?

370
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:21,120
Of course.

371
00:23:21,680 --> 00:23:23,640
If Lu Xia defeats me next time,

372
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:26,480
I will publish a comic book
with him as the villain.

373
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:30,160
I can't defeat him in a match,
but I can in my drawings.

374
00:23:31,080 --> 00:23:32,080
[chuckles]

375
00:23:32,440 --> 00:23:33,320
[sighs]

376
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:35,120
Don't move.

377
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:38,120
It distracts me from the composition.

378
00:23:41,840 --> 00:23:43,480
You've been drawing me for a whole day.

379
00:23:44,560 --> 00:23:46,440
I can't endure it anymore.

380
00:23:47,240 --> 00:23:49,240
It's almost done. One final touch.

381
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:57,840
[exhales sharply]

382
00:23:58,840 --> 00:24:00,840
[quirky music]

383
00:24:06,840 --> 00:24:08,920
How is it? Isn't it good?

384
00:24:16,600 --> 00:24:19,480
Is this me?

385
00:24:20,760 --> 00:24:23,040
Yes. What's wrong?
Doesn't it look like you?

386
00:24:25,760 --> 00:24:27,520
[Huang Jing] They're very alike. Huh?

387
00:24:27,760 --> 00:24:30,800
I used techniques of realism.
How vivid it is!

388
00:24:33,520 --> 00:24:35,760
You drew pretty fast.
Let me have a look. Quick.

389
00:24:37,560 --> 00:24:38,560
[Xiuwen sighs]

390
00:24:41,600 --> 00:24:42,480
Mm-hm?

391
00:24:45,520 --> 00:24:47,240
[coughs]

392
00:24:53,480 --> 00:24:56,440
[Huang Jing] Xiuwen, I think that...

393
00:24:57,480 --> 00:24:58,760
we are not suitable for the arts.

394
00:25:00,200 --> 00:25:02,360
[boy sobbing]

395
00:25:03,960 --> 00:25:05,360
[sobbing continues]

396
00:25:06,280 --> 00:25:08,280
[boy whimpering]

397
00:25:26,560 --> 00:25:30,080
Hey kid, why are you crying here?
Be tough like a man.

398
00:25:30,640 --> 00:25:33,520
I'm still young,
so I can cry when I feel unhappy.

399
00:25:34,280 --> 00:25:36,680
[boy] I had confidence
in my abilities in sports,

400
00:25:36,760 --> 00:25:41,440
however, he suddenly showed up
and made a mess of me.

401
00:25:43,800 --> 00:25:45,320
I don't want to join the race.

402
00:25:45,760 --> 00:25:47,120
Hey, hey, hey.

403
00:25:47,360 --> 00:25:51,560
Hey, be a man and accept the result.

404
00:25:52,240 --> 00:25:55,280
Even though you lost this time,
you can win next time.

405
00:25:56,320 --> 00:26:00,320
You don't understand
how important this race was to me.

406
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:02,600
[boy] I could have won the championship.

407
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:05,680
I could have joined
the track and field team.

408
00:26:06,240 --> 00:26:08,720
I have practiced a lot for this day.

409
00:26:10,120 --> 00:26:11,840
Do you like running so much?

410
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:13,280
Of course.

411
00:26:13,840 --> 00:26:17,560
I don't spend my free time
on animations and games,

412
00:26:17,800 --> 00:26:19,880
[boy] I spend it on practicing running.

413
00:26:20,560 --> 00:26:24,480
Because you love running so much,
you must not give up so easily.

414
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:27,920
Let me ask you. Why do you like running?

415
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:30,720
I've been running fast since I was young.

416
00:26:31,000 --> 00:26:32,080
[Baiyang chuckles]
That's it.

417
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:34,560
You like running because you run fast.

418
00:26:35,040 --> 00:26:39,160
For those who really love running,
even if they naturally run slow,

419
00:26:39,560 --> 00:26:44,240
they will run faster and become stronger
because of their love for running.

420
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:48,600
Do you mean people run fast
because they love running?

421
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:49,520
Mm-hm.

422
00:26:50,040 --> 00:26:52,880
Hey, is there any sport you like?

423
00:26:54,680 --> 00:26:56,040
Me?

424
00:26:56,800 --> 00:26:57,640
[soft chuckle]

425
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:04,080
[Baiyang] Here you are.

426
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:13,240
Can you teach me
how to play tennis next time?

427
00:27:13,320 --> 00:27:16,000
[Baiyang] I will teach you
after you win first place in the marathon.

428
00:27:23,200 --> 00:27:25,200
[traffic noise]

429
00:27:27,760 --> 00:27:29,040
It really is different.

430
00:27:29,120 --> 00:27:31,760
[Siyang] You need to think about
how to break your record

431
00:27:32,600 --> 00:27:34,240
using your past experiences.

432
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:38,360
Someday, you can play tennis
in your own style.

433
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:44,200
[Ying] Aunt, I'm in the office right now.
Where is your package?

434
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:50,560
Okay, I will find it on my own.

435
00:27:54,760 --> 00:27:55,680
Why are you here?

436
00:27:56,240 --> 00:27:58,280
I came to pick up a package for my aunt.

437
00:27:58,920 --> 00:28:00,400
There it is.

438
00:28:01,200 --> 00:28:02,160
[sighs]

439
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:04,000
[thwacks]

440
00:28:08,080 --> 00:28:10,240
You can leave the key.
I will lock the door.

441
00:28:12,280 --> 00:28:13,160
It's okay.

442
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:16,960
I will wait for you.

443
00:28:19,600 --> 00:28:21,440
[breathes deeply]

444
00:28:21,920 --> 00:28:23,920
[crowd cheering on TV]

445
00:28:27,760 --> 00:28:29,080
[thwacking on TV]

446
00:28:30,480 --> 00:28:31,960
Can you get my jacket?

447
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:39,760
-This one?
-Please put it on.

448
00:28:41,640 --> 00:28:43,000
[soft chuckle]

449
00:28:44,120 --> 00:28:46,120
[light music]

450
00:28:53,040 --> 00:28:54,280
[thwacking]

451
00:28:59,320 --> 00:29:01,040
The girl you like?

452
00:29:01,720 --> 00:29:03,200
[Qiao Chen] The girl you like.

453
00:29:04,120 --> 00:29:06,120
[quirky music]

454
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,200
[inhales sharply]

455
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:10,440
I want to ask you a question.

456
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:12,040
You can return it tomorrow.

457
00:29:14,440 --> 00:29:16,120
I don't mean this.

458
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:20,480
On the way to school on that day,

459
00:29:20,960 --> 00:29:23,560
I saw you and Qiao Chen.

460
00:29:24,720 --> 00:29:28,080
You seemed to be
talking about a girl, right?

461
00:29:29,560 --> 00:29:30,520
What's wrong?

462
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:34,680
Hmm. I overheard your conversation.

463
00:29:34,760 --> 00:29:35,840
Well...

464
00:29:37,200 --> 00:29:38,440
Well...

465
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:42,440
What happened to you and her?

466
00:29:43,280 --> 00:29:44,840
I just confirmed it with him.

467
00:29:45,560 --> 00:29:46,880
What did he say?

468
00:29:47,720 --> 00:29:49,200
He didn't reply to me clearly.

469
00:29:49,520 --> 00:29:50,600
[gasps]

470
00:29:52,600 --> 00:29:53,480
[sighs]

471
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:58,880
That must happen all the time.

472
00:30:00,520 --> 00:30:02,320
Don't take it to heart.

473
00:30:02,880 --> 00:30:03,720
Mmm.

474
00:30:04,280 --> 00:30:07,480
Even if he leaves now,
he will return to the club someday.

475
00:30:09,920 --> 00:30:10,800
Huh?

476
00:30:12,400 --> 00:30:13,320
The tennis club?

477
00:30:14,120 --> 00:30:15,160
Who are you talking about?

478
00:30:17,800 --> 00:30:18,640
I mean the captain.

479
00:30:21,600 --> 00:30:23,280
[giggles]

480
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:28,400
I'll leave the keys and your jacket here.
I shall leave now.

481
00:30:28,480 --> 00:30:29,520
Don't put on...

482
00:30:35,360 --> 00:30:37,960
[giggling]

483
00:30:39,840 --> 00:30:41,560
I see.

484
00:30:42,280 --> 00:30:43,720
[chuckles]

485
00:30:43,800 --> 00:30:45,800
[light music]

486
00:30:59,120 --> 00:31:00,200
[cell phone dings]

487
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:06,160
[Jingwu] Your appointment in the hospital
will be in ten days.

488
00:31:06,600 --> 00:31:09,040
I arranged the accommodations
and bought a plane ticket for you.

489
00:31:09,120 --> 00:31:10,840
Someone will pick you up at the airport.

490
00:31:12,520 --> 00:31:13,480
[Siyang] Thank you.

491
00:31:17,800 --> 00:31:18,760
[sighs]

492
00:31:20,040 --> 00:31:23,000
[Dayong] Are you really going abroad?

493
00:31:23,440 --> 00:31:24,280
Yes.

494
00:31:26,320 --> 00:31:28,480
Though the situation
was stable temporarily,

495
00:31:29,480 --> 00:31:30,840
I still want to use my left arm...

496
00:31:32,600 --> 00:31:34,640
and join the national tournament
with you all.

497
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:35,600
I understand.

498
00:31:38,200 --> 00:31:39,080
[Siyang sighs]

499
00:31:39,960 --> 00:31:41,040
[gasps]

500
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:46,880
By the way,
though Xinglong started training again,

501
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:49,640
please pay attention to his hand injury.

502
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:52,400
[Siyang] Don't let him
force himself too much.

503
00:31:53,520 --> 00:31:57,040
Qiao Chen tends to underestimate
his rivals.

504
00:31:58,160 --> 00:32:01,200
Though he played pretty well
in the last match,

505
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:04,120
remember to let him keep training.

506
00:32:04,520 --> 00:32:05,680
Don't let him give up easily.

507
00:32:07,040 --> 00:32:11,440
Baiyang tends to be stubborn.

508
00:32:12,560 --> 00:32:15,160
[Siyang] When he goes too far,
we should help him know when to stop.

509
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:19,040
Zhuo Zhi...

510
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:20,600
I want to be like you.

511
00:32:21,840 --> 00:32:22,960
Ignore the consequences...

512
00:32:23,760 --> 00:32:24,640
and never regret.

513
00:32:25,120 --> 00:32:26,000
[chuckles]

514
00:32:26,080 --> 00:32:28,560
Let's leave his problems
for him to figure out.

515
00:32:29,160 --> 00:32:30,160
Leave him alone.

516
00:32:30,480 --> 00:32:32,480
[somber music]

517
00:32:33,200 --> 00:32:34,160
Oh.

518
00:32:35,200 --> 00:32:36,160
As for Huang Jing,

519
00:32:37,080 --> 00:32:39,880
among members of Grade 11,
he plays relatively better.

520
00:32:41,040 --> 00:32:42,320
[Siyang] During regular training,

521
00:32:42,640 --> 00:32:45,280
remember to train him as a main player.

522
00:32:46,520 --> 00:32:48,840
For Xiuwen and Mu,

523
00:32:49,600 --> 00:32:53,520
both of them have a strong passion
for tennis.

524
00:32:55,320 --> 00:32:57,320
In addition to basic training,

525
00:32:57,800 --> 00:33:00,400
remember to give them
more chances to join matches.

526
00:33:04,560 --> 00:33:05,680
As for Lu Xia...

527
00:33:06,760 --> 00:33:08,240
I want to be Yu Qing's pillar.

528
00:33:11,080 --> 00:33:13,560
If it is necessary, you can rely on him.

529
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:19,920
For you and Jiale...

530
00:33:27,040 --> 00:33:29,280
Jiale has made great progress recently.

531
00:33:29,960 --> 00:33:31,120
As his partner,

532
00:33:31,680 --> 00:33:34,040
you can't give up no matter what.

533
00:33:34,640 --> 00:33:38,720
You have to support each other
and become better Golden Partners.

534
00:33:39,760 --> 00:33:40,720
Don't worry.

535
00:33:41,440 --> 00:33:42,800
I won't run anymore.

536
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:45,960
I'll count on you

537
00:33:46,360 --> 00:33:47,480
as the acting captain.

538
00:33:48,560 --> 00:33:49,880
[Siyang] During my leave,

539
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:53,600
please take care of the team.

540
00:33:54,560 --> 00:33:56,200
I won't let you down.

541
00:33:58,360 --> 00:34:00,080
[inhales sharply]
Okay.

542
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:02,160
[sighs]

543
00:34:08,560 --> 00:34:09,560
Siyang.

544
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:13,280
Coach Qi, everything is settled.

545
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:16,600
But you didn't give them a chance
to say goodbye?

546
00:34:18,400 --> 00:34:19,360
Sure.

547
00:34:20,120 --> 00:34:22,040
Go ahead. They are waiting for you.

548
00:34:23,760 --> 00:34:25,960
Coach Qi, thank you.

549
00:34:47,199 --> 00:34:49,199
[somber music]

550
00:34:54,560 --> 00:34:56,400
-[Qiao Chen] Captain.
-[Baiyang] Captain.

551
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:58,159
-[He Xinglong] Captain.
-[Lu Xia] Captain.

552
00:35:09,520 --> 00:35:14,080
It is my dream to lead us
to the national tournament.

553
00:35:14,760 --> 00:35:17,120
But I can't do that on my own.

554
00:35:19,440 --> 00:35:20,400
[Siyang] No matter what,

555
00:35:21,320 --> 00:35:23,360
we will enter the finals
of the nationals together.

556
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:28,000
I have never changed my will
from the beginning.

557
00:35:28,600 --> 00:35:29,840
So I invite everyone

558
00:35:30,120 --> 00:35:32,400
to keep the promise we have made

559
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:35,200
and fight until the very end.

560
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:40,320
Yu Qing.

561
00:35:45,520 --> 00:35:46,600
[all] Winner!

562
00:35:50,560 --> 00:35:51,600
Thank you all.

563
00:35:52,440 --> 00:35:54,440
[somber music]

564
00:36:06,560 --> 00:36:07,480
[Dayong] Assemble.

565
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:20,760
[Tang Jiale] Captain.

566
00:36:22,160 --> 00:36:24,960
Are you really leaving?

567
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:27,920
-Dachi.
-Yes.

568
00:36:28,760 --> 00:36:30,440
Isn't it training time now?

569
00:36:30,520 --> 00:36:31,360
Yes.

570
00:36:31,520 --> 00:36:34,200
-But we all want to--
-Provincial finals are around the corner.

571
00:36:34,720 --> 00:36:36,120
Have you slacked off?

572
00:36:37,840 --> 00:36:39,840
-Twenty laps for everyone.
-But, Captain, today you--

573
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:41,080
What are you waiting for?

574
00:36:42,200 --> 00:36:44,200
[somber music]

575
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:07,960
[somber music continues]

576
00:37:13,720 --> 00:37:15,080
[Siyang] I saw everyone was growing

577
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:17,960
since the beginning
of the regulation match.

578
00:37:19,240 --> 00:37:21,320
About you and Lu Xia,

579
00:37:22,240 --> 00:37:23,600
I don't need to worry at all.

580
00:37:24,280 --> 00:37:25,720
I chose to believe in them,

581
00:37:26,080 --> 00:37:28,640
so I have to believe
that no matter what happens,

582
00:37:29,520 --> 00:37:30,640
there is always a way out.

583
00:37:32,880 --> 00:37:33,920
[Siyang] I'll count on you.

584
00:37:39,600 --> 00:37:41,280
[all panting]

585
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,400
[breathing heavily]

586
00:38:03,600 --> 00:38:05,480
GO, YU QING

587
00:38:11,920 --> 00:38:12,880
Captain.

588
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:16,320
Did he leave?

589
00:38:17,920 --> 00:38:19,040
Nineteen laps to go.

590
00:38:20,720 --> 00:38:21,720
Go, Yu Qing!

591
00:38:23,560 --> 00:38:24,520
[all] Go!

592
00:38:25,080 --> 00:38:27,080
[light music]

593
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:36,080
♪ Flying higher and higher to the sky ♪

594
00:38:36,600 --> 00:38:40,320
♪ With clouds floating
And dancing in the wind ♪

595
00:38:41,280 --> 00:38:45,600
♪ I'm not afraid of setback and defeat ♪

596
00:38:46,200 --> 00:38:49,400
♪ There's nothing that can beat me ♪

597
00:38:50,040 --> 00:38:53,520
♪ I don't care the cold shoulder and sneer
From the others ♪

598
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:58,400
♪ Despite all kinds
Of hardships and difficulties ♪

599
00:38:59,040 --> 00:39:03,320
♪ I will make you proud of me ♪

600
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:06,920
♪ And throw myself into your arms ♪

601
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:11,400
GO, YU QING

