00:39:21,040 --> 00:39:22,240
[sighs]

603
00:39:22,920 --> 00:39:24,680
[crickets chirping]

604
00:39:33,840 --> 00:39:35,320
[Sha] Don't worry too much, Coach Qi.

605
00:39:36,120 --> 00:39:37,080
[sighs]

606
00:39:38,600 --> 00:39:39,800
Though Siyang left,

607
00:39:40,600 --> 00:39:42,120
Yu Qing's vigor will never die out.

608
00:39:43,160 --> 00:39:44,240
I'm not worried.

609
00:39:45,400 --> 00:39:47,120
I feel quite lucky

610
00:39:47,800 --> 00:39:49,560
to be with these kids.

611
00:39:51,720 --> 00:39:53,520
They are so energetic

612
00:39:54,520 --> 00:39:57,160
in the pursuit of their dreams.

613
00:39:57,240 --> 00:39:58,520
[Coach Qi] I've become more aware

614
00:39:58,600 --> 00:40:01,840
of how important
the life and soul of a team is.

615
00:40:02,840 --> 00:40:03,760
If he stays,

616
00:40:04,760 --> 00:40:06,120
he can bring strength to the team.

617
00:40:06,640 --> 00:40:07,640
If he leaves,

618
00:40:08,840 --> 00:40:11,720
he can leave hope for the team.

619
00:40:13,120 --> 00:40:16,680
I heard that, when Lu Xiangqian
was in Yu Qing,

620
00:40:16,760 --> 00:40:18,040
your father was his coach.

621
00:40:18,440 --> 00:40:21,680
That's why you pay so much attention
to Lu Xia's progress, right?

622
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:27,160
When Lu Xiangqian was abroad,
he called me once.

623
00:40:28,280 --> 00:40:30,120
He said that Lu Xia is a genius,

624
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:32,480
a good tennis player,

625
00:40:33,040 --> 00:40:34,240
and the future of tennis.

626
00:40:35,080 --> 00:40:39,880
But he should first be happy,

627
00:40:40,600 --> 00:40:42,200
be able to be touched,

628
00:40:42,680 --> 00:40:44,640
and make people touched.

629
00:40:46,760 --> 00:40:51,160
Otherwise, all the glory is meaningless.

630
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:53,280
[Coach Qi] In fact,

631
00:40:53,680 --> 00:40:56,400
I can understand
Lu Xiangqian's anxiety then.

632
00:40:57,760 --> 00:40:59,120
I also agree with him.

633
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:01,800
Tennis...

634
00:41:02,360 --> 00:41:04,400
is a long journey through life.

635
00:41:06,040 --> 00:41:09,240
It's not the end goal of some quest.

636
00:41:10,160 --> 00:41:13,520
I feel that, after joining Yu Qing,

637
00:41:13,880 --> 00:41:17,880
Lu Xia has changed a lot,
though he still looks isolated.

638
00:41:17,960 --> 00:41:19,800
[both chuckle]

639
00:41:20,680 --> 00:41:24,000
Oh. By the way, I was curious then,

640
