on interviewing Yu Qing's players.

641
00:41:29,400 --> 00:41:34,440
Actually, when the chief editor asked me
to interview junior tennis players,

642
00:41:34,520 --> 00:41:35,640
I was very reluctant.

643
00:41:36,200 --> 00:41:38,720
My dream was to become
a top sports reporter.

644
00:41:39,640 --> 00:41:42,520
I thought I should interview
the best sports stars.

645
00:41:42,600 --> 00:41:43,760
That was more practical.

646
00:41:45,080 --> 00:41:45,960
But after,

647
00:41:46,560 --> 00:41:48,320
