one after another.

650
00:41:55,440 --> 00:41:59,200
[Sha] I realized that shouting
because of being moved

651
00:41:59,640 --> 00:42:01,680
and smiling because of winning

652
00:42:02,760 --> 00:42:04,520
are not so different.

653
00:42:05,840 --> 00:42:07,000
