655
00:42:09,640 --> 00:42:11,760
[soft chuckle]
I'm happy that you feel that way.

656
00:42:13,000 --> 00:42:15,680
Yu Qing needs to keep progressing.

657
00:42:16,800 --> 00:42:18,880
And so do you.

658
00:42:21,240 --> 00:42:23,640
-Keep it up!
-Thank you, Coach Qi.

